    %p.text-center.xmb
      %strong Last updated:
      21 October, 2018

    %p
      This privacy policy is for this website
      = "[#{link_to 'https://www.mindfullifetherapy.co.uk', 'https://www.mindfullifetherapy.co.uk'}]".html_safe
      and is served by
      %strong Mindful Life Therapy
      and governs the privacy of its users who choose to use it.
      The policy sets out the different areas where user privacy is concerned and outlines the obligations & requirements of the users, the website and website owner.
      Furthermore the way this website processes, stores and protects user data and information will also be detailed within this policy.

    %h2.mmb The Website
    %p
      This website and its owner take a proactive approach to user privacy and ensure the necessary steps are taken to protect the privacy of its users throughout their visiting experience. This website complies to all UK national laws and requirements for user privacy.

    %h2.mmb Use of Cookies
    %p
      This website uses cookies to better the user's experience while visiting the website.
    %p
      Cookies are small files saved to the user's hard drive that store information about the user's interactions and usage of the website.
      This allows the website, through its server to provide the users with a tailored experience within the website.
    %p
      Users are advised that if they wish to deny the use and saving of cookies from this website on to their hard drive they should take necessary steps within their web browser security settings to block all cookies from this website and its external serving vendors.

    %h2.mmb Contact & Communication
    %p
      Users contacting this website and / or its owner do so at their own discretion and provide any such personal details requested at their own risk. Your personal information is kept private and stored securely until a time it is no longer required or has no use, as detailed in the Data Protection Act 1998. Every effort has been made to ensure a safe and secure form to contact the website owner, but you use it at your own risk.
    %p
      This website and its owner use any information submitted to provide you with further information about the services they offer or to assist you in answering any questions or queries you may have submitted.
      Your details are not passed on to any third parties.

    %h2.mmb External Links
    %p
      Although this website only looks to include quality, safe and relevant external links, users are advised to adopt a policy of caution before clicking any external web links mentioned throughout this website. (External links are clickable text / banner / image links to other websites.)
    %p
      The owner of this website cannot guarantee or verify the contents of any externally linked website despite their best efforts. Users should therefore note they click on external links at their own risk and this website and its owner cannot be held liable for any damages or implications caused by visiting any external links mentioned.

    %h2.mmb Social Media Platforms
    %p
      Communication, engagement and actions taken through external social media platforms that this website and its owner participate on are custom to the terms and conditions as well as the privacy policies held with each social media platform respectively.
    %p
      Users are advised to use social media platforms wisely and communicate / engage upon them with due care and caution in regard to their own privacy and personal details. This website nor its owner will ever ask for personal or sensitive information through social media platforms and encourage users wishing to discuss sensitive details to contact them through primary communication channels such as by telephone or email.
    %p
      This website may use social sharing buttons which help share web content directly from web pages to the social media platform in question. Users are advised before using such social sharing buttons that they do so at their own discretion and note that the social media platform may track and save your request to share a web page respectively through your social media platform account.

    %h2.mmb Shortened Links in Social Media
    %p
      This website and its owner through their social media platform accounts may share web links to relevant web pages. By default some social media platforms shorten lengthy urls [web addresses].

    %p
      Users are advised to take caution and good judgement before clicking any shortened urls published on social media platforms by this website and its owner. Despite the best efforts to ensure only genuine urls are published many social media platforms are prone to spam and hacking and therefore this website and its owner cannot be held liable for any damages or implications caused by visiting any shortened links.

